longBusinessSummary: Firma Holdings Corp. does not have significant operations. Previously, the company was engaged in mining, packaging technology, and food manufacturing businesses. It intends to focus on emerging and middle market domestic and international investment opportunities. The company was formerly known as Tara Minerals Corp. and changed its name to Firma Holdings Corp. in June 2014. Firma Holdings Corp. was founded in 2006 and is based in Henderson, Nevada.
